3.title: Boise vs. Chicago

episode of.title: A Sale of Two Cities (TV Series 2014– )

3.plot: Johnny and Erin have been married for ten years. They're a quintessential Air Force couple, relocating every few years. Now that Johnny is being stationed in Boise, the couple wants to buy a house they can call home. Meanwhile, entrepreneur and bachelor Mauricio has been living with roommates in Chicago for several years. He's finally ready to ditch the roommates and buy a place of his own in the Windy City. Both sets of home buyers have the same $400,000 budget. But who will get the best value for their dollar?
